# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment variables — copy this file to .env and fill in values
# NEVER commit .env to git (it is listed in .gitignore)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# EmailJS — https://dashboard.emailjs.com
#
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT: VITE_ prefixed variables are BUNDLED INTO THE
#    CLIENT-SIDE JS by Vite. They are readable in browser DevTools.
#    This is expected for EmailJS (the public key is designed to be
#    public). Protect your account by enabling Domain Allowlisting
#    in the EmailJS dashboard: Service → Settings → Allowed Origins.
#
VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
